The following sections supplement the ones in the main INSTALL text for the iOS port. An ARMv7 device running at least iOS 6.0 is required to run Imagine.

1. Tools and Environment Setup
==============================

The following environment variables are used by the build system:

CCTOOLS_TOOCHAIN_PATH : Optional, default taken from environment variable
 - The path to ported cctools toolchain for building on Linux, see https://github.com/tpoechtrager/cctools-port

XCODE_PATH : Optional, defaults to $(shell xcode-select --print-path)
 - The path in the Xcode app bundle containing the "Platforms/" subdirectory
 
IOS_SDK : Optional, if not set the first SDK directory found is used
 - The version of the SDK in Xcode to use as the sysroot

